      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Lull e..2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>綠兮衣兮，綠衣黃裳，心之憂矣，曷維其亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Green is the upper robe;
Green the upper, and yellow the lower garment!
The sorrow of my heart, —
How can it be forgotten?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
