      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Lull e..4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>絺兮綌兮，淒其以風，我思古人，實獲我心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Linen, fine or coarse,
Is cold when worn in the wind.
I think of the ancients,
And find what is in my heart.</seg>
      </tuv>
